  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess whether a tailored diet, eliminating antigens to which
      IgA nephropathy patients have demonstrated sensitivity, will have an effect on proteinuria,
      renal function and other immunological variables.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
